data.text: @ELLEmagazine As usual when it comes to Bieber & Gomez, only one team's narrative is being reported in the gossip news cycle, which itself is a dumpster trough of fake news, copy & paste churnalism and non-firsthand sourced claims repeated by sites for clickbait.
